/-- The factor f_i(γ) = 1 - γ tᵢ + γ² dᵢ is minimised at γ = tᵢ/(2dᵢ),
    where f_i(tᵢ/(2dᵢ)) = 1 - tᵢ²/(4dᵢ) = (4dᵢ - tᵢ²)/(4dᵢ).

    For a PSD 2×2 matrix with tr = tᵢ, det = dᵢ:
      tᵢ² ≥ 4dᵢ  (AM-GM on eigenvalues)
    So f_i ≥ 0, with minimum ≥ 0 at γ = tᵢ/(2dᵢ). -/
